<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
China, Hainan Province: Bawangling National Forest Park, on diseased leaves of 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Sterculiaceae" genus="Pterospermum" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Pterospermum heterophyllum" order="Malvales" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="heterophyllum">
